B.S7=new A.bJ(B.xG,["Welcome!","Enter your name to start memorizing representatives.","First Name","Language","Representatives","Start","Cancel","Change","Delete","Add Profile","Who's Learning?","Browse","Quiz","Results","Settings","Search members...","Search members...","Filter","Sort","Sort by Last Name","Sort by Least Memorized","Sort by Most Memorized","Party","Region","All","Practice Subset","Mode","Name Match","Choose the name for a face","Party Match","Choose the party for a face","Riding Match","Choose the riding for a face","Name Recall","Type the last name for a face","Face Match","Identify the face for last name","Last Name","Riding","Select Riding:","Correct!","Incorrect!","Answer: ","Next","Finish","Score","No members found with these filters. Please loosen your criteria.","No members found.","No quiz results to show yet.","Duplicate Last Names","Duplicate","Proceed","Credits","\ud83d\ude80 Data & Web Services","Thanks to ","OpenNorth"," for their great Represent API. \ud83c\udf0d","\ud83c\udfdb\ufe0f Legislative Assemblies","As well, thanks to each of the legislative assembly websites from across Canada.","\ud83d\ude4c Special Thanks","Finally, big thanks to Gavin Davis and Owen Mackenzie (HoC Pages 2026-2027) for their feedback in developing this app. \ud83d\udca1","\ud83d\udcec Feedback welcome!","Issues","Privacy","Privacy Policy","This application respects your privacy. \n\n1. Data Collection: We collect minimal data necessary for the app to function, including your chosen first name and quiz results. \n\n2. Storage: Data is stored locally on your device and synchronized with our secure Firebase backend for leaderboard and progress tracking purposes. \n\n3. Third Parties: We use Firebase (a Google service) for data storage and hosting. No data is sold to third parties. \n\n4. Your Rights: You can delete your local data at any time via the Settings menu. For backend data deletion, contact us at guydavis.ca@gmail.com. \n\n5. Compliance: This policy is designed to comply with Canadian privacy standards (PIPEDA).","Close","Loading representatives...","Enhancing with latest status..."],t.li)
B.S8=new A.bJ(B.xG,["Bienvenue!","Entrez votre nom pour commencer \xe0 m\xe9moriser les repr\xe9sentants.","Pr\xe9nom","Langue","Repr\xe9sentants","D\xe9marrer","Annuler","Changer","Supprimer","Ajouter un profil","Qui apprend?","Parcourir","Quiz","R\xe9sultats","Param\xe8tres","Rechercher des membres...","Rechercher des membres...","Filtrer","Trier","Trier par nom de famille","Moins m\xe9moris\xe9","Plus m\xe9moris\xe9","Parti","R\xe9gion","Tous","Sous-ensemble de pratique","Mode","Association de Noms","Choisissez le bon nom pour un visage","Association de Partis","Choisissez le bon parti pour un visage","Association de Circonscriptions","Choisissez la circonscription pour un visage","Rappel de Noms","Tapez le nom pour un visage","Association de Visages","Identifiez le visage pour un nom de famille","Nom de famille","Circonscription","S\xe9lectionnez la circonscription:","Correct!","Incorrect !","R\xe9ponse : ","Suivant","Terminer","Score","Aucun membre trouv\xe9 avec ces filtres. Veuillez assouplir vos crit\xe8res.","Aucun membre trouv\xe9.","Aucun r\xe9sultat de quiz \xe0 afficher pour le moment.","Noms de famille en double","Double","Continuer","Cr\xe9dits","\ud83d\ude80 Donn\xe9es et Services Web","Merci \xe0 ","OpenNorth"," pour leur excellente API Represent. \ud83c\udf0d","\ud83c\udfdb\ufe0f Assembl\xe9es l\xe9gislatives","De plus, merci \xe0 chacun des sites Web des assembl\xe9es l\xe9gislatives du Canada.","\ud83d\ude4c Remerciements sp\xe9ciaux","Enfin, un grand merci \xe0 Gavin Davis et Owen Mackenzie (HoC Pages 2026-2027) pour leurs commentaires lors du d\xe9veloppement de cette application. \ud83d\udca1","\ud83d\udcec Les commentaires sont les bienvenus !","Probl\xe8mes","Confidentialit\xe9","Politique de confidentialit\xe9","Cette application respecte votre vie priv\xe9e. \n\n1. Collecte de donn\xe9es : Nous collectons le minimum de donn\xe9es n\xe9cessaires au fonctionnement de l'application, y compris le pr\xe9nom de votre choix et les r\xe9sultats des quiz. \n\n2. Stockage : Les donn\xe9es sont stock\xe9es localement sur votre appareil et synchronis\xe9es avec notre backend Firebase s\xe9curis\xe9 \xe0 des fins de classement et de suivi des progr\xe8s. \n\n3. Tierces parties : Nous utilisons Firebase (un service Google) pour le stockage et l'h\xe9bergement des donn\xe9es. Aucune donn\xe9e n'est vendue \xe0 des tiers. \n\n4. Vos droits : Vous pouvez supprimer vos donn\xe9es locales \xe0 tout moment via le menu Param\xe8tres. Pour la suppression des donn\xe9es du backend, contactez-nous \xe0 guydavis.ca@gmail.com. \n\n5. Conformit\xe9 : Cette politique est con\xe7ue pour se conformer aux normes canadiennes de protection de la vie priv\xe9e (LPRPDE).","Fermer","Chargement des repr\xe9sentants...","Am\xe9lioration avec le dernier statut..."],t.li)
